{"tid":1637763,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"26人暴動 坐四年","createTime":"2019-10-08T05:41:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T08:13:05.000Z","uid":170438,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"718af09a52ebb689eb09c3acb24dbe34b7f3f348","tid":1637763,"uid":170438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:41:29.000Z","msg":"慘呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n26人涉灣仔參與暴動及違禁止蒙面　下午西九法院提堂<br />\n2019-10-08 HKT 13:08<br />\n 分享工具\t facebook  twitter<br />\n警方再控告26人參與暴動，年齡最小13歲。案件下午在西九龍裁判法院提堂，是《禁止蒙面規例》上周六生效後，第二批被檢控個案。<br />\n<br />\n警方在剛過去的星期日晚上，在灣仔拘捕14名本地男子及12名本地女子，年齡介乎13至33歲。經調查及諮詢法律意見後，26人分別被暫控一項「參與暴動」罪，當中14人分別暫被加控一項「違反《禁止蒙面規例》」罪。"},{"pid":"7448ac51ed483a9d685fcc840d06bbc38ea78c65","tid":1637763,"uid":145267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:42:48.000Z","msg":"坐4年？？"},{"pid":"b889ce4055295fdafd0c6e9f685074bce7c0d705","tid":1637763,"uid":36813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:44:21.000Z","msg":"屌你 個四年邊撚到黎阿 仆街"},{"pid":"de8ac9758f0c3c9c67f3dc435f6178627327ac23","tid":1637763,"uid":284630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:45:13.000Z","msg":"蒙面罪同期執行<br />\n同埋果日港島火魔法都唔多個, 黑警點會有證據落暴動<br />\n問律政司點搞, 律政司鳩告左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c1243c170cd7520d172acf7b2429b0ad4b1489a","tid":1637763,"uid":320814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:47:17.000Z","msg":"不推文回覆"},{"pid":"f724dcd735dfffafc4e3c7a5c4fa92dd84ab921b","tid":1637763,"uid":320814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:48:18.000Z","msg":"不推文回覆"},{"pid":"a03090ef64f23992598d1c2804fb07330dabc3cc","tid":1637763,"uid":8562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:50:23